		{"id":"legend","type":"text","text":"# 🗺️ Event Storming — Operational & Cross-Context (F)\n\nUse cases **F1–F4**: GDPR company purge, provider token sync, scheduling history audit, and the bounded-context hand-off to recording infrastructure. These are the background, cross-cutting, and integration concerns — not directly user-initiated.\n\n**Colour key** — 🟧 Event · 🟦 Command · 🟩 Actor/System · 🟥 Policy · 🟪 Service · ⬛ Data store","x":-3180,"y":-1120,"width":1600,"height":200,"color":"6"},
