		{"id":"note_f4","type":"text","text":"**The bounded-context boundary.**\n`call-scheduling-updated` is the **Published Language** (OHS).\nCRUD=NEW → recording enabled.\nCRUD=CANCEL → recording stopped.\nCRUD=UPDATE → recording adjusted.\n\nSee [[Subsystems/Call Scheduling/Canvas/Bounded Context Map - Call Scheduling & Consent.canvas|Bounded Context Map]]","x":-1000,"y":740,"width":440,"height":218,"color":"6"}
